query:
SELECT DISTINCT RECIPENAME, TOOLNAME
FROM 
      (SELECT Z_PK AS RECIPEID, ZNAME AS RECIPENAME, ZTOOL 
       FROM ZRECIPE JOIN (SELECT Z_PK AS PRIMARYKEY, ZRECIPE, ZTOOL FROM ZRECIPETOOL) 
       WHERE RECIPEID = ZRECIPE), 
      (SELECT Z_PK AS TOOLID, ZNAME AS TOOLNAME, ZRECIPE 
       FROM ZTOOL JOIN (SELECT Z_PK AS PRIMARYKEY, ZRECIPE, ZTOOL FROM ZRECIPETOOL) 
       WHERE TOOLID = ZTOOL) 
WHERE ZTOOL = TOOLID AND ZRECIPE = RECIPEID
